qm guest exec $VMID -- stat /mnt/data
```

### Cloud-init

```bash
qm guest exec $VMID -- cloud-init status
qm guest exec $VMID -- tail -50 /var/log/cloud-init-output.log
```

## SSH доступ

```bash
